[Quotes]
victory1 = "It's best to crush insects quickly once they've gotten inside, right?"
victory2 = "Whatever. I'll just consume them. As they become my flesh and blood, they will see beyond. I... I am the king!"
victory3 = "Anyone who looks at me like they're underestimating my power, I'll smash every one of 'em into oblivion!"
victory4 = "Come on. The one who remains standing will return alive. That's all it comes down to!"
victory5 = "Like I'd lose... like I'd... there's no way... no way I'd lose to someone like you!"
victory6 = "Damn right. Who you are has nothing to do with killing you!"

